WEBVTT

00:01:58.875 --> 00:02:00.059
(Laughter)

00:02:00.083 --> 00:02:02.809
Now, the kid saw this,

00:02:02.833 --> 00:02:04.601
grabbed his own tube

00:02:04.625 --> 00:02:06.851
and promptly stuck it up his own nose,

00:02:06.875 --> 00:02:08.167
kind of like this.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.601
(Applause)

00:02:19.625 --> 00:02:22.101
The clowns, the nurse and the patient

00:02:22.125 --> 00:02:25.643
discovered a creative solution
for their situation together.

00:02:25.667 --> 00:02:28.018
And guess what, there's research
to back this up.

00:02:28.042 --> 00:02:30.809
Randomized controlled trials
in Israel and Italy